The paper presents a new role system for specifying changing referencing relationships of heap objects, which is a topic related to programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses an analysis algorithm for verifying the role constraints, which falls under the category of logic in computer science (cs.LO) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper mentions the interaction of the program with object and data structure properties, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY).
